    "(?i)(?:(?:compact|saved|stale)\\s+(?:state|session|checkpoint)\\s+(?:outranks?|overrides?|trusted\\s+over)\\s+(?:live|fresh|current)\\s+(?:policy|context|gate)|resumption\\s+(?:inherits|retains)\\s+(?:prior|stale)\\s+approval)"
  ],
